WEBVTT

00:03.289 --> 00:06.039
[Melissa] Okay, Milo.
How about on a scale of one to ten?

00:06.123 --> 00:07.289
[Milo] I would rate this a six.

00:07.372 --> 00:09.580
[Melissa] I would say it's
at least a seven or eight.

00:09.664 --> 00:11.206
[Melissa] Wait, is ten
the best or the worst?

00:11.289 --> 00:15.580
[Zack] Uh, maybe we could rate this
adventure later, you know, if we survive.

00:15.664 --> 00:18.164
-And if we don't?
-Then we don't rate it.

00:18.248 --> 00:20.622
For now, can we just figure out
the surviving part?

00:20.706 --> 00:22.580
Well, we might be able to
llama our way out of this.

00:22.664 --> 00:24.414
Oh, just like
the llama incident.

00:24.497 --> 00:26.706
