08:32.330 --> 08:35.872
Melissa! I just remembered that Diogee
is one quarter llama dog.

08:35.956 --> 08:37.123
What does that even mean?

08:37.206 --> 08:40.081
He herds llamas
like a sheep dog herds sheep.

08:40.164 --> 08:41.164
I've never seen
him do that.

08:41.248 --> 08:43.580
Oh, yeah. It just doesn't
come up very often.

08:43.664 --> 08:46.248
[speaking Spanish]

08:46.330 --> 08:48.831
