Since when do you know Spanish?

08:48.914 --> 08:49.914
Well...

08:49.998 --> 08:51.706
[speaking Spanish]

08:51.789 --> 08:53.081
[speaking Spanish]

08:53.164 --> 08:56.081
Okay, okay, but how does Diogee
know Spanish?

08:56.164 --> 08:57.123
Well...

08:57.206 --> 09:00.539
[speaking Spanish]

09:01.248 --> 09:02.580
