-Okay.

09:04.831 --> 09:07.081
[speaking Spanish]

09:07.164 --> 09:09.164
[Diogee barking]

09:17.206 --> 09:18.956
Good boy.

09:19.039 --> 09:21.289
Now, jump.

09:21.372 --> 09:24.872
No, I meant Melissa,
but you're right, that was ambiguous.

09:24.956 --> 09:26.164
Melissa, jump!

09:26.248 --> 09:27.497
Are you sure?

09:27.580 --> 09:28.706
Trust me.

09:29.289 --> 09:31.123
[exclaims]

09:32.206 --> 09:33.956
Oh, they're so soft.

09:34.039 --> 09:36.039
They're not like
a briefcase at all.

09:36.123 --> 09:37.248
I know, right?

09:37.330 --> 09:39.539
-[blows whistle]
-[whooping]

09:39.622 --> 09:41.497
And that was
the llama incident.

09:41.580 --> 09:44.539
Wow, no wonder you guys made a big deal
about that story.

09:44.622 --> 09:46.164
Yeah, it was legendary.

09:46.248 --> 09:47.622
